text:
The staff were happily chatting away, Ignoring customer order.

When Interrupted gave a very rude stare and tone.

When questioned about the food just brush it off with a nonchalant answer.

Food quality ok, but you can definitely find a better Malay food stall within this vicinity

Beef fried rice with 4 slices of beef.. Pathetic.
Sotong with Thai sauce.. not crispy at all.. waste of money
Bought seafood fried Rice, this time the squid size of cumi..its OKlah but totally soft like spoilt. This Crabmeat soft & smaller than loose corn. OMG last time not like that but price the same..

Waited 30 mins for my walk-in order. But end up only 2 out 4 dishes were prepared. Cashier doesnâ€™t take care of orders. So some people who came later, got their food. And grab orders got settled first. Terrible lah. If you have a lot of time to wait, come here. If not, get ready to wait long long.
There was hair in my food and my family food e.g the veggies felt undercooked as it was hard. Usually its better.
